<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Consultation Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color:
      #f4f6f8; margin: 0; padding: 20px; color: #333; } .email-container {
      max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h2 {
      color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 12px; } p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 8px
      0; } ul { padding-left: 18px; margin: 10px 0; } li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
      a { color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; } a:hover { text-decoration:
      underline; } .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff !important; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none; margin: 12px 0; font-weight: bold; } .footer {
      margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #555; border-top: 1px solid
      #eee; padding-top: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <p>Dear <b>{{customerName}}</b>,</p>

      <p>
        Great news! Your doctor consultation is officially booked. You're all
        set to chat with
        <b>{{doctorName}}</b>. We're so excited for you to get the care you
        deserve!
      </p>

      <h2>Appointment Details</h2>
      <p><b>Date:</b> {{date}}</p>
      <p><b>Time:</b> {{startTime}} - {{endTime}}</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{joinUrl}}" class="btn">Join Consultation</a>
      </p>
      <p><b>Meeting ID:</b> {{meetingId}}</p>
      <p><b>Password:</b> {{password}}</p>

      <h2>How to Prepare for Your Consultation</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Make sure you have a stable internet connection.</li>
        <li>Find a quiet, well-lit space for your video call.</li>
        <li>
          Write down any questions or concerns you have for the doctor
          beforehand.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        ðŸ’¡ Quick Tip: Find a quiet, comfy spot a few minutes before your call so
        you're ready to go.
      </p>

      <p>
        We can't wait to help you on your health journey. Stay healthy and
        happy!
      </p>

      <p><b>Warm regards,</b><br />The Mobilab2u Care Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Have questions? Contact our support team at
          <a href="mailto:info@mobilab2u.com">info@mobilab2u.com</a>
          or visit our FAQ page. | Mobilab2u
        </p>

        <p>From,</p>
        <p>Administration Team,</p>
        <p><b>Mobilab2u.com</b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>